      "content": "That's a fair distinction. When you mention \"shifting community composition\" in Profile B as a source of uncertainty, are you suggesting that changes in the racial or ethnic makeup of a neighborhood typically act as a negative driver for property value stability? Just trying to understand the specific risk factors you're weighing here.",
